headline: Synchrony Names Deborah Ellinger to Board of Directors
summary: Synchrony Financial (NYSE: SYF), a premier consumer financial services company, today announced Deborah Ellinger, a former CEO and experienced board member with extensive experience across multiple industries, including health and wellness and retail, has been appointed to Synchrony's Board of Directors, effective October 1, 2025.
